--- cyrus-imapd-2.1.13.orig/fink/cyrus-makedirs	Wed Dec 31 17:00:00 1969
+++ cyrus-imapd-2.1.13/fink/cyrus-makedirs	Thu Jun 19 09:44:02 2003
